name: 95Q Crybaby Q
details:
Q control wah with auto-return switchingWe've taken the original Cry Baby Wah and added three of our most popular upgrades: the famous Q Control, which varies the intensity of the wah effect by adjusting the effect's bandpass shape; Volume Boost, for up to +15dB added gain; and our Auto-Return function that automatically engages the effect when you place your foot on the pedal. It all adds up to a versatile, great sounding wah.
